{"lemma":"بَلاغَةٌ","slug":"بَلاغَةٌ","root":"ب.ل.غ","root_slug":"ب-ل-غ","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-ل-غ","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n3239"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D9%8E%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%BA%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of بَلُغَ (baluḡa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"rhetoric"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"eloquence"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun of بَلُغَ (baluḡa)."},"ipa":["/ba.laː.ɣa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n3239","headword_ar":"بَلَاغَةٌ","root":"blg","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSaAHapN","text_ar":"فَصَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Eloquence;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baluga","text_ar":"بَلُغَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", of which it is the inf. n.;)] (S, Msb, *) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bilagonN","text_ar":"بِلَغْنٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Seer, TA.) ―         -b2-  And [the pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaAgaAtN","text_ar":"بَلَاغَاتٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Slanders,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"calumnies."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%A8%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%BA%D8%A9/","headword_ar":"بلاغة","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_18","lexicon_en":"Al-Sharīf al-Jurjānī, Kitāb al-Taʿrīfāt (d. 1413 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب التعريفات للشريف الجرجاني","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=23023#43edf7","body_html":"<span>البلاغة في المتكلم: ملكة يقتدر بها إلى تأليف كلام بليغ، فعلم أن كل بليغ؛ كلامًا كان، أو متكلمًا، فصيح؛ لأن الفصاحة مأخوذة في تعريف البلاغة، وليس فصيح بليغًا.<br></span><br><div>البلاغة في الكلام: مطابقته لمقتضى الحال. والمراد بالحال: الأمر الداعي إلى التكلم على وجه مخصوص مع فصاحته، أي فصاحة الكلام.</div><div><br></div><div>وقيل: البلاغة: تنبؤ عن الوصول والانتهاء، يوصف بها الكلام والمتكلم فقط، دون المفرد.</div>"}]}}